metadata.title: Ethereum Golden Pocket In Play – Can ETH Turn The Tide Above $2,800?
metadata.description: Ethereum is testing a critical juncture as the golden pocket between $2,600 and $2,800 comes into play. With resistance looming at $2,800, the market now faces a pivotal moment. Can ETH reclaim this level and spark a move toward $3,000, or will sellers push it back below key support?Golden Pocket B…
